~ start_cow_box
box: [[Hi|Hello]], your animals seem hungry!
box: Do you want to feed your cow?
- yes: 
	Kitty: Yes, it needs food!
	do GameDialogueManager.action_feed_animals()
- No: 
	Kitty: No, I don't want to feed it!
=> END

~ start_chicken_box
box: [[Hi|Hello]], your animals seem hungry!
box: Do you want to feed your chicken?
- yes: 
	Kitty: Yes, it needs chicken feed!
	do GameDialogueManager.action_feed_animals()
- No: 
	Kitty: No, it just wants to play basketball!
=> END